   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VVrS11.16 Var. b (ms. 4045):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> sē guftan parāhōm xwardan pad sē bār ud harw bār rāspīg-iz <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> dō guftan parāhōm pad panǰ ud dō ud dō abāz xwardan dahān pāk kardan
            dast harw dō pad pādyāb kardan dast ī hōy abar barsom nihādan</ab>  
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "He should  recite three times the <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em> and drink the <em>parāhōm</em> in three times. Each time, the <em>rāspīg</em> should also recite two <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em>.
            He should drink the <em>parāhōm</em> in portions of two and two fifths. The <em>zōt</em> should clean his mouth und wash his both hands with <em>pādyāb</em> and put his
            left hand on the <em>barsom</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
